        "description": "Standard range for 1064 nm cleaning; higher rates (50-100 kHz) speed up process but risk heat accumulation in low-conductivity concrete. Recommended 50 kHz for balanced throughput and thermal management. Source: Academic literature in J. Clean. Prod. (2021) on industrial laser parameters for building materials."
